California ignition interlock installation locations
Getting back on the road is fast and easy with the #1 provider in California. Begin your ignition interlock device installations and our customer experience representatives will schedule your appointment for you at a convenient installation center at the time you choose with a certified ignition interlock device (car breathalyzer, BAIID, IID, interlock system) installer. Service centers include: Los Angeles, Glendale, Pasadena, Huntington Beach, Anaheim, Santa Barbara and many more.  We make it easy, read our DUI checklist for California and find installation locations near you.  

 


 











