blow & drive interlock corp
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Automotive
Sub-Industry: Auto Parts
Blow & Drive Interlock Corporation develops and distributes ignition interlock devices. The Company offers an alcohol ignition interlock device that is installed on the steering column of vehicles to prevent drunk driving. Blow & Drive markets its products in the United States, Canada, and Australia.




