                            By  |
                            











Blow & Drive Interlock Corporation is a publicly traded company on the OTCQB (BDIC) and is a
provider of automotive and criminal offender monitoring security products. BDIC is making
tremendous progress because our state‐of‐the‐art ignition interlock device BDI-747 is
approved and available in 8 states for evidentiary as well as preliminary screening use. Our state
of the art BDI-747 is the most advanced user friendly IID currently available which can record BAC
levels, offers 2 way communication, GPS location technology, image technology and is
wireless.
We have begun a second run of an additional 1,000 BDI-747 to meet our high demand and prepare for major national expansion. We continue to apply for additional State Certifications and hope to have the BDI-747 available to customers nationwide. We believe our share of the global market can rise steadily. In addition, we continue to do research and development of the next stage of offender monitoring which we believe will be smartphone enabled monitoring apps that could reduce or completely eliminate the need for ankle bracelets, or hand held breathalyzers.

