Blow & Drive Interlock Corp.


            
            Blow & Drive Interlock Corp. is a development stage company, which engages in lawful corporate undertaking, including, but not limited to, selected mergers and acquisitions. The company was founded on July 2, 2013 and is headquartered in Beverly Hills, CA.

            
